title: New: Golden Vessel – Do You Think About Me (ft. MTNS)
body:
Dream collaboration from two of Australia’s finest talents – **MTNS** and **Golden Vessel**.

_Do You Think About Me_ is a silky smooth production; perfect for the forthcoming warmer days. Check it below.

Follow our [On Repeat Playlist](https://open.spotify.com/user/crackintheroad/playlist/1UB6gJIZpmiO0H2zmSbg02) for a handpicked selection of the very best in new music; updated weekly.
